<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a4May1933"><font color="red">4 May 1933</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Valery Larbaud): I wondered whether your flat would be rentible during June-August. I should like a small quiet flat to work in all the summer while my wife is house-hunting and then to move into fixed quarters about September </div>
